HEADWORD: Accadian
<hw>Ac*ca"di*an</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[From the city
<ets>Accad</ets>. See Gen. x. 10.]</ety> <def>Pertaining to a race
supposed to have lived in Babylonia before the Assyrian
conquest.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

